Who sent you to destroy me?

0:00:53.080,0:00:57.800
In the name of Jesus Christ!

0:01:00.640,0:01:05.540
At the name of Jesus Christ every spirit must bow.

0:01:05.540,0:01:08.960
Rise up, in the name of Jesus!

0:01:12.400,0:01:16.600
The man rises to his feet and the spiritual battle continues.

0:01:16.600,0:01:20.880
Your back on the floor!

0:01:20.880,0:01:27.140
