0:01:35.760,0:01:36.980
I'm destroying you?

0:01:36.980,0:01:37.780
Yes.

0:01:37.780,0:01:40.940
Who are you?

0:01:40.940,0:01:44.400
I'm the lion.

0:01:44.400,0:01:46.220
The lion?

0:01:46.220,0:01:49.220
You want to touch me? OK, touch me if you can touch.

0:01:49.220,0:01:51.280
Just touch and see.

0:01:51.280,0:01:56.620
The man possessing a spirit of the lion arches his fingers like claws,

0:01:56.620,0:02:01.860
and moves forward in an attempt to touch the man of God, prophet T.B. Joshua.

0:02:01.860,0:02:07.460
He gets into a position and moves closer to grab the man's of God leg.

0:02:07.460,0:02:09.020
But look at his hand!

0:02:09.020,0:02:11.380
