0:02:30.340,0:02:32.340
Watch!

0:02:34.560,0:02:40.120
Stop that! In the name of Jesus, stop it!

0:02:40.120,0:02:44.440
Many of you are toys in their hands.

0:02:44.440,0:02:52.240
They can only run from light.

