0:06:15.500,0:06:19.880
have been defeated by the mighty power of Jesus Christ.

0:06:19.880,0:06:26.760
Emotions begin to flow as Jesus Christ has put an end to his past, and he is now a new creation

0:06:26.760,0:06:29.280
in Christ Jesus.

