0:07:02.060,0:07:03.740
Glory be to God.

0:07:03.740,0:07:05.440
Stand up.

0:07:07.400,0:07:09.740
To God be the glory.

0:07:14.560,0:07:16.560
Thank You, Jesus!

0:07:16.560,0:07:18.640
I am free, in Jesus' name.

0:07:23.700,0:07:25.120
Here he comes.

0:07:25.120,0:07:30.860
Put your hands together for Jesus.

