Emmanuel! God is with us. (Matthew 1:23)

0:07:35.320,0:07:40.720
My name is Chinedu Nwosu. I come from Abia state, Nigeria.

0:07:40.720,0:07:43.080
This is my mum.

0:07:43.080,0:07:46.780
I thank God for what He has used Prophet T.B. Joshua to do in my life,

0:07:46.780,0:07:53.020
for delivering me from the world of darkness we had gone into.

0:07:53.020,0:07:56.580
I was possessed with a demon.

0:07:56.580,0:08:01.280
I was a dragon in my world then.

0:08:01.280,0:08:06.260
Now, I've been delivered by Prophet T.B. Joshua

0:08:06.260,0:08:11.300
into this real world which God has placed me in.

0:08:11.300,0:08:19.000
And the powers I had then were so many.

0:08:19.000,0:08:24.060
I used those powers to sleep with people.

0:08:24.060,0:08:29.580
I'd dream. Sometimes, the person would feel that their husband

0:08:29.580,0:08:33.120
was having fun with them but he's not.

0:08:33.120,0:08:39.160
I'd make the husband be like wood lying in the bed while I had fun with them.

0:08:39.160,0:08:40.860
Those are spiritual husbands.

0:08:40.860,0:08:44.860
Spiritual husbands come in two ways.

0:08:44.860,0:08:51.560
One comes from the marine world where I came from and one comes physically.

0:08:51.560,0:08:55.240
Then their husband would be nothing to them anymore.

0:08:55.240,0:09:04.200
But I thank God that Prophet T.B. Joshua has delivered me from this world of darkness.

0:09:04.200,0:09:11.880
I used the power of lion to put fear in people; they couldn't look at my face.

0:09:11.880,0:09:22.800
If they were about 15 to 30 trying to bring me down, I'd bring all of them down because they were nothing.

0:09:22.800,0:09:26.980
All of them would be like dead rats in my sight.

0:09:26.980,0:09:31.560
I would make sure I pulled every power they had down.

0:09:31.560,0:09:35.620
If care was not taken, sorry would be their name.

0:09:35.620,0:09:41.600
I would bring them down because the power in me didn’t come from me alone

0:09:41.600,0:09:44.060
but from the world of darkness.

0:09:44.060,0:09:54.520
If you feel that the world of darkness is not real, the devil is not real - the devil exists.

0:09:54.520,0:10:00.200
There is not any other power more than the blood of Jesus Christ.

0:10:00.200,0:10:09.460
When I came to the SCOAN I was at the prayer line and Prophet T.B. Joshua touched me.

0:10:09.460,0:10:14.640
When he touched me, it was just like burning fire.

0:10:14.640,0:10:19.240
When he came a second time, I couldn't withstand him.

0:10:19.240,0:10:22.340
The spirit in me couldn't withstand it.

0:10:22.340,0:10:28.300
He asked me if I wanted to fight him and I was bold enough to tell him that I wanted to fight him.

0:10:28.300,0:10:29.540
Do you want to fight me?

0:10:29.540,0:10:31.140
Yes.

0:10:31.140,0:10:32.520
Who sent you to destroy me?

0:10:32.520,0:10:33.340
Who?

0:10:33.340,0:10:35.360
Who sent you to destroy me?

0:10:35.360,0:10:39.280
In the name of Jesus Christ!

0:10:43.020,0:10:45.600
Assuming I pulled him down,

0:10:45.600,0:10:48.780
that would've been the glory to the kingdom world.

0:10:48.780,0:10:54.600
But he beat me to the end.

0:10:54.600,0:11:00.320
He made sure that the he proved that the blood of Jesus Christ saves.

0:11:03.740,0:11:07.540
In the mighty name of Jesus Christ!

0:11:07.540,0:11:10.120
I declare you free!

0:11:10.120,0:11:14.160
Contrary spirit, out!

0:11:14.160,0:11:15.420
Out!

0:11:15.420,0:11:16.400
In Jesus Christ's name!

