Watch your screen.

0:11:18.400,0:11:20.220
You are free.

0:11:20.220,0:11:25.540
In the end, I was delivered. I was just like a dead lion.

0:11:25.540,0:11:35.840
Now at this moment, I give thanks to God because I am back to my original self that I was.

0:11:35.840,0:11:42.220
There is something that I saw in the man of God, Prophet T.B. Joshua.

0:11:42.220,0:11:46.460
There is a great light covering him so I could not hurt him.

0:11:46.460,0:11:51.340
The Lord, God Almighty has used Prophet T.B Joshua to deliver me.

0:11:51.340,0:11:55.980
I'm free and I'm free forever.

0:11:58.460,0:12:00.320
Emmanuel! (God with us – Matthew 1:23)

0:12:00.320,0:12:03.140
Thank God for saving my son.

0:12:03.140,0:12:10.680
My name is Mrs Mercy Nwosu. I am the mother of Chinedu.

0:12:10.680,0:12:15.900
My testimony goes like this. Chinedu is my son.

0:12:15.900,0:12:19.740
When I gave birth to him, he was a good child.

0:12:19.740,0:12:22.640
During his school age years, he was good

0:12:22.640,0:12:32.760
